=\"hkgmoji\" />搵咗勁耐先耐到隻佢肯食嘅，但次次開比佢佢又食得唔多，勁擔心佢第時有腎病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw 你講嘅呢個款exact7ly係我考慮緊個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:49:52.000Z","msg":"除咗水機之外，有無嘗試喺屋企唔同位置放水碗，都可以吸引貓貓飲水"},{"pid":"dd7f1de151d9493fbcb7f0872a4434c93c64222c","tid":2181711,"uid":253451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"746a110cbf5be2d5b9995ad2b98be405d6dd0029","tid":2181711,"uid":328654,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T08:29:13.000Z","msg":"想問下有冇人用過呢隻花花飲水機？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HnedQqY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHnedQqY.png&h=054daf40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己好鐘意不過唔知貓b會唔會用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見hktv買得好平下， 心思思想買"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"有用啊，不過係方形，夜晚個燈會好光，所以收埋咗喺機裡面海綿位置，就好啲。我屋企隻貓由4個月大入屋開始就用水機，換過1部，但第一部唔係花花機，佢好快就知道水機飲水，應該引導一下就可以<br />\nP. S. 水機強烈建議根據產品說明書，每星期洗一次！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"4931a95ccad907774752c310b21785f21576d654","tid":2181711,"uid":11034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af555ea78f69909604eba3c53aa2a2d847458a23","tid":2181711,"uid":28997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c1b4db53482859f9a4302fa9b523503e5e60f88","tid":2181711,"uid":264641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T19:04:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nK1vOaV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnK1vOaV.png&h=1bda9937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽講有隻漏電"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T19:16:42.000Z","msg":"非打手 我之前都有研究過呢隻<br />\n佢漏電版本係2腳插/大陸版多<br />\n新版本用USB/所謂香港行貨就好似無呢個問題<br />\n不過點都係大陸野 自己衡量"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T16:51:58.000Z","msg":"全部水機都有，係感應電<br />\n唔洗擔心既<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wjFSo7yuBF8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwjFSo7yuBF8&d=lPj0fEAhrWG